OL,3,CBus driver who killed two mums in
OL,4,C'tragic accident' avoids jail
OL,6,FA bus driver has avoided jail after
OL,7,Fkilling two mothers in a "tragic
OL,8,Faccident".
OL,10,FJoyce Bacon, 60, and Adele Boylin, 55,
OL,11,Fwere standing waiting to board the bus
OL,12,Fin Piccadilly Gardens, in Manchester,
OL,13,Fwhen they were hit by a double decker.
OL,15,FBaruania Baros, a bus driver of four
OL,16,Fyears experience with a clean driving
OL,17,Flicence, was helping a disabled
OL,18,Fpassenger leave the bus when he
OL,19,Faccidentally pressed the accelerator
OL,20,Finstead of the brake pedal.
