OL,3,CBus driver who killed two mums in
OL,4,C'tragic accident' avoids jail
OL,6,FThe bus jolted forward and crashed
OL,7,Finto the women, causing fatal injuries.
OL,9,FBaros, 35, from Ashton-under-Lyne,
OL,10,Fpleaded guilty to two counts of
OL,11,Fcausing death by careless driving, and
OL,12,Fwas given a suspended prison sentence.
OL,14,FThe judge said his pregnant wife would
OL,15,Fbe harmed if Baros was locked up, and
OL,16,Fruled that he did not pose a 'risk or
OL,17,Fdanger' to the public.
OL,19,FProsecutors told how Baros had worked
OL,20,Fas a driver for Stagecoach since
OL,21,FFebruary 2019.
