OL,3,CBus driver who killed two mums in
OL,4,C'tragic accident' avoids jail
OL,6,FHe was driving down Oldham Road in the
OL,7,FNorthern Quarter in Manchester city
OL,8,Fcentre, before turning left onto
OL,9,FPiccadilly Gardens at about 9.20pm on
OL,10,FJuly 10, 2022.
OL,12,FMr and Mrs Bacon and their friend Ms
OL,13,FBoylin, a mother-of-four who worked at
OL,14,FManchester Royal Eye Hospital and was
OL,15,Fmaking her way home after a shift,
OL,16,Fwere standing waiting to take the bus
OL,17,Fhome when Baros arrived.
OL,19,FAfter pulling over at the bus stop,
OL,20,FBaros went to help a passenger on a
OL,21,Fmobility scooter to leave the bus.
