OL,3,CBus driver who killed two mums in
OL,4,C'tragic accident' avoids jail
OL,6,FThe court heard that he had to park at
OL,7,Fan angle because another bus had been
OL,8,Fin front of him.
OL,10,FBaros then got out of the bus to pull
OL,11,Fout the access ramp, but it could not
OL,12,Fbe used due to the angle of the bus.
OL,14,FHe then got back into the bus and
OL,15,Fdecided to raise the level of the
OL,16,Fvehicle instead. Prosecutors said he
OL,17,Freleased the handbrake and the bus
OL,18,Fmoved forwards.
