OL,6,FHe then went to hit the brake, but
OL,7,Finstead put his foot down on the
OL,8,Faccelerator, crashing into Mrs Bacon
OL,9,Fand Ms Boylin as they waited to board
OL,10,Fthe bus.
OL,12,FAn expert found that Baros had left
OL,13,Fthe bus in gear, rather than in
OL,14,Fneutral as it should have been. If it
OL,15,Fhad been left in neutral, the accident
OL,16,Fwould have been avoided, the court
OL,17,Fheard.
