OL,3,CBus driver who killed two mums in
OL,4,C'tragic accident' avoids jail
OL,6,F"This was a fatal mistake on your
OL,7,Fpart," Judge Suzanne Goddard KC told
OL,8,FBaros, describing the incident as a
OL,9,F'tragic accident'.
OL,11,FBoth women were rushed to the
OL,12,FManchester Royal Infirmary after
OL,13,Fsuffering serious injuries.
OL,15,FMrs Bacon died that evening, while Ms
OL,16,FBoylin remained in hospital until she
OL,17,Fpassed away on December 6, 2022.
