OL,6,F"You Baruania Baros will carry the
OL,7,Fburden of knowing your actions caused
OL,8,Ftheir deaths for the rest of your
OL,9,Flife, and their families will feel the
OL,10,Fterrible tragic effects of your
OL,11,Fnegligence for the rest of their
OL,12,Flives," Judge Goddard said.
OL,14,FIan Bacon, Mrs Bacon's husband, told
OL,15,Fthe court of his devastation at the
OL,16,Floss of his wife of 15 years. "Joyce
OL,17,Fand I did everything together," he
OL,18,Fsaid.
