OL,6,F"She was my best friend as well as my
OL,7,Fwife. Following the loss of Joyce I
OL,8,Fhave struggled deeply with coming to
OL,9,Fterms with living my life without her."
OL,11,FIn a statement read on her behalf, Ms
OL,12,FBoylin's daughter Sophie said: "The
OL,13,Fday that my mother was struck by a bus
OL,14,Fwas the start of the end of life as I
OL,15,Fknew it."
OL,17,FShe added: "The last thing she said to
OL,18,Fme was that she loved me and she would
OL,19,Fspeak to me tomorrow. I keep wishing
OL,20,Fthat that tomorrow would happen."
