OL,6,FThe court heard that Baros and his
OL,7,Ffamily arrived in the UK as part of a
OL,8,Frefugee program, after spending time
OL,9,Fdetained in a refugee camp in Tanzania.
OL,11,FHe married in 2020 and his wife is due
OL,12,Fto give birth in the next few weeks,
OL,13,FBaros' barrister Patrick Cassidy said.
OL,15,FMr Cassidy said that Baros had no
OL,16,Frecord of disciplinary action prior to
OL,17,Fhis dismissal from Stagecoach, and had
OL,18,Fsubmitted testimonials which spoke
OL,19,Fwell of him and told of his remorse.
